'''埃拉·科尔特兰·金尼·賽蒙'''（Ellar Coltrane Kinney Salmon，{{bd|1994年|8月27日}}）是一名[[美国|美国]]男演员<ref>{{cite web|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|title=10 Most Buzzed-About Sundance Actors, From Bill Hader to Maika Monroe|url=http://www.thewrap.com/sundance-2014-buzzed-about-actors-bill-hader|publisher=The Wrap|accessdate=26 April 2014|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216140316/https://www.thewrap.com/sundance-2014-buzzed-about-actors-bill-hader/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Zuckerman|first=Esther|title=Talking About the Nostalgia of 'Boyhood' with its Star, Ellar Coltrane|url=http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/07/ellar-coltrane-of-boyhood-on-nostalgia/374194/|publisher=The Wire|accessdate=11 July 2014|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013638/http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/07/ellar-coltrane-of-boyhood-on-nostalgia/374194/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，生于德州[[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]。

==事业==
